Scorponok


   Scopronok is slammed by the autoguns into the sheilds. He starts
to 
go into Statius lock but he fights it off. He grabs his remote out of 
the backpack he was wearing. He then took off his back pack and threw 
it at the group of predacons. He then pressed the trigger on the 
remote making the bombs explode. Yelling at the Predacon base he 
says,"Where is QuickStrike and Darkmouse!!!" Scorponok starts to run 
into the forest for his life, coughing mech fluid all over the place.

  He calls the Predacon cave on his com while he is on the run, 
"Predacon C(Cough Cough)ave...P(cough)redacon Cave...Pl(cough)ease 
come in....I ne(cough)ed help..."
